---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/main.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer';
import { baseUrl } from '../../lib/base-url';

const pageClass = 'programs-page';
---

<MainLayout pageClass={pageClass}>
  <Header client:only="react" />
  
  {/* Hero Section */}
  <section style="position: relative; height: 400px; background-image: url(https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1503676260728-1c00da094a0b?w=1600&q=80); background-size: cover; background-position: center; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;">
    <div style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0; background-color: rgba(11, 42, 111, 0.75);"></div>
    <div style="position: relative; z-index: 10; text-align: center; color: #F7F3EA; max-width: 900px; padding: 0 24px;">
      <h1 style="font-family: var(--heading-font); font-size: 56px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #F7F3EA;">Academic Programs</h1>
      <p style="font-family: var(--body-font); font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.6; color: #F7F3EA;">From infancy through elementary, a seamless path of joyful learning</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* Overview */}
  <section style="background-color: #F7F3EA; padding: 96px 24px;">
    <div style="max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center;">
      <h2 style="font-family: var(--heading-font); font-size: 48px; color: #123EAB; margin-bottom: 32px; font-weight: 600;">A Developmentally Appropriate Journey</h2>
      <p style="font-family: var(--body-font); font-size: 20px; color: #26303D; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 24px;">
        At St. Mark's, we believe in meeting children where they are. Our programs are designed to honor each stage of development while building strong academic, spiritual, and character foundations.
      </p>
      <p style="font-family: var(--body-font); font-size: 20px; color: #26303D; line-height: 1.8;">
        We combine the best of Montessori methods for our youngest learners with a rigorous classical Christian curriculum for elementary students.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* Program Cards */}
  <section style="background-color: #FCFBF7; padding: 96px 24px;">
    <div style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(450px, 1fr)); gap: 48px;">
        
        {/* Early Childhood Card */}
        <div style="background-color: #F7F3EA; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.12); border: 1px solid #D8D2C4;">
          <div style="height: 280px; background-image: url(https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1587654780291-39c9404d746b?w=800&q=80); background-size: cover; background-position: center;"></div>
          <div style="padding: 40px;">
            <h3 style="font-family: var(--heading-font); font-size: 36px; color: #123EAB; margin-bottom: 16px; font-weight: 600;">Early Childhood</h3>
            <p style="font-family: var(--body-font); font-size: 18px; color: #C8A64E; margin-bottom: 20px; font-weight: 600;">Infants – Kindergarten</p>
            <p style="font-family: var(--body-font); font-size: 17px; color: #26303D; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 24px;">
              Our Montessori-inspired early childhood program creates a nurturing environment where young children develop independence, wonder, and a love of learning through hands-on exploration and play.
            </p>
            <ul style="font-family: var(--body-font); font-size: 16px; color: #26303D; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 32px; padding-left: 20px;">
              <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Infant & Toddler Care (6 weeks – 3 years)</li>
              <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Preschool (Ages 3-4)</li>
              <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Pre-K & Kindergarten (Ages 4-6)</li>
              <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Montessori-trained teachers</li>
              <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Multi-age classrooms</li>
              <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Hands-on learning materials</li>
            </ul>
            <a href={`${baseUrl}/programs/early-childhood`} style="display: inline-block; background-color: #123EAB; color: #F7F3EA; font-family: var(--button-font); font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; transition: opacity 0.2s;">
              Learn More →
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Elementary Card */}
        <div style="background-color: #F7F3EA; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.12); border: 1px solid #D8D2C4;">
          <div style="height: 280px; background-image: url(https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1546410531-bb4caa6b424d?w=800&q=80); background-size: cover; background-position: center;"></div>
          <div style="padding: 40px;">
            <h3 style="font-family: var(--heading-font); font-size: 36px; color: #123EAB; margin-bottom: 16px; font-weight: 600;">Elementary</h3>
            <p style="font-family: var(--body-font); font-size: 18px; color: #C8A64E; margin-bottom: 20px; font-weight: 600;">Grades 1 – 6</p>
            <p style="font-family: var(--body-font); font-size: 17px; color: #26303D; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 24px;">
              Our classical Christian elementary program builds strong foundations in language, mathematics, history, science, and the arts while cultivating virtue, wisdom, and a heart for God.
            </p>
            <ul style="font-family: var(--body-font); font-size: 16px; color: #26303D; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 32px; padding-left: 20px;">
              <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Grammar Stage (Grades 1-3)</li>
              <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Logic Stage (Grades 4-6)</li>
              <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Latin & classical languages</li>
              <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Great Books curriculum</li>
              <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Integrated humanities approach</li>
              <li style="margin-bottom: 8px;">Small class sizes</li>
            </ul>
            <a href={`${baseUrl}/programs/elementary`} style="display: inline-block; background-color: #123EAB; color: #F7F3EA; font-family: var(--button-font); font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; transition: opacity 0.2s;">
              Learn More →
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* Daily Schedule Preview */}
  <section style="background-color: #F7F3EA; padding: 96px 24px;">
    <div style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <h2 style="font-family: var(--heading-font); font-size: 42px; color: #123EAB; margin-bottom: 48px; text-align: center; font-weight: 600;">A Day in the Life</h2>
      
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 48px;">
        <div style="background-color: #FCFBF7; padding: 40px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #D8D2C4;">
          <h3 style="font-family: var(--heading-font); font-size: 28px; color: #123EAB; margin-bottom: 24px; font-weight: 600;">Morning</h3>
          <p style="font-family: var(--body-font); font-size: 17px; color: #26303D; line-height: 1.8;">
            Each day begins with prayer and morning circle time, followed by focused academic work in core subjects when young minds are most alert and receptive.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div style="background-color: #FCFBF7; padding: 40px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #D8D2C4;">
          <h3 style="font-family: var(--heading-font); font-size: 28px; color: #123EAB; margin-bottom: 24px; font-weight: 600;">Afternoon</h3>
          <p style="font-family: var(--body-font); font-size: 17px; color: #26303D; line-height: 1.8;">
            Afternoons include enrichment activities such as art, music, physical education, and outdoor exploration, balancing rigorous academics with joyful play.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {/* CTA Section */}
  <section style="background-color: #123EAB; padding: 80px 24px; text-align: center;">
    <div style="max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <h2 style="font-family: var(--heading-font); font-size: 42px; color: #F7F3EA; margin-bottom: 24px; font-weight: 600;">Ready to Learn More?</h2>
      <p style="font-family: var(--body-font); font-size: 20px; color: #F7F3EA; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 32px;">
        Schedule a visit to see our classrooms in action and meet our dedicated faculty.
      </p>
      <div style="display: flex; gap: 16px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
        <a href={`${baseUrl}/admissions/visit`} style="display: inline-block; background-color: #F7F3EA; color: #123EAB; font-family: var(--button-font); font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; padding: 16px 40px; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none;">
          Schedule a Visit
        </a>
        <a href={`${baseUrl}/admissions/inquire`} style="display: inline-block; background-color: transparent; color: #F7F3EA; border: 2px solid #F7F3EA; font-family: var(--button-font); font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; padding: 14px 40px; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none;">
          Inquire Now
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer client:only="react" />
</MainLayout>
